This is a patch for CloneFunction, InlineFunction:

[Inline][CloneAndPruneFunctionInto] Consider the nonnull argument for…
… null check
diff --git a/llvm/include/llvm/Transforms/Utils/Cloning.h b/llvm/include/llvm/Transforms/Utils/Cloning.h
